# Fork Conventions

## Component Library is Read-Only

Files in `components/ui/` are the shared foundation across all GAB verticals. Never create, modify, or delete files in this directory. If a component is missing or needs changes, open an issue on the boilerplate repository.

## Where to Put New Code

### Page-specific compositions → `_components/`

Components that are specific to a single page live next to that page:

```
app/(dashboard)/my-feature/
├── page.tsx                  # Server Component: fetch data, pass props
└── _components/
    └── MyDashboard.tsx       # 'use client': render using atoms/molecules/organisms
```

### Fork-level shared components → `components/_custom/`

If a fork needs a reusable component not in the boilerplate:

```
components/
├── ui/          # NEVER MODIFY
└── _custom/     # Fork-specific shared components
```

`_custom/` components must compose from `@/components/ui/` imports — never recreate what already exists.

## Banned Patterns

- **No alternative UI libraries.** Never install MUI, Chakra, Ant Design, or any other component library. Everything is built on Radix UI + Tailwind.
- **No inline styles.** Never use `style={{}}`. Use Tailwind utility classes via `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`.
- **No custom CSS files.** No `.css` or `.scss` files outside of `app/globals.css`. All styling is Tailwind.
- **No copy-paste customization.** Never copy a component from `components/ui/` to modify it. Use the component's existing props and variants. If the props don't cover your case, that's a signal to request an upstream enhancement.

## Import Rules

Always import from barrel exports:

```typescript
import { Button, Badge } from '@/components/ui/atoms';
import { Card, DataTable } from '@/components/ui/molecules';
import { DataGrid, Navbar } from '@/components/ui/organisms';
import { DashboardLayout } from '@/components/ui/layouts';
```

Never import from internal component files directly (e.g., `@/components/ui/atoms/Button`).
